label: subject part concept scheme
definition: a SKOS concept scheme for ac:subjectOrientation

label: unspecified part
definition: Part is not known because it is not specified

label: entire organism
definition: An entire multicellular organism

label: bark
definition: Plant tissue outside the vascular cambium

label: twig
definition: Plant shoot axis developed from axillary buds

label: stem
definition: Plant shoot axis that defines the primary axis

label: leaf
definition: Plant non-reproductive phyllome

label: strobilis (cone)
definition: Plant reproductive system consisting of sporophylls

label: inflorescence
definition: Plant reproductive shoot system containing flowers

label: fruit
definition: Plant structure developing from a flower

label: seed
definition: Plant structure containing dormant embryo

label: male cone
definition: Plant strobilis bearing pollen

label: female cone
definition: Plant strobilis bearing ovules

label: flower
definition: Plant reproductive shoot system containing a carpel

label: head
definition: Anterior-most division of the body

label: thorax
definition: The middle division of the insect body bearing locomotor appendages

label: abdomen
definition: The posterior-most division of the insect body

label: leg
definition: Walking appendage

label: wing
definition: Appendage that is shaped in order to produce lift for flight through the air

label: antenna
definition: The paired, usually multiple jointed, sensory organs on the head

label: forewing
definition: The paired insect wing that is continuous with the mesonotum

label: hindwing
definition: The paired insect wing that is continuous with the metanotum

label: foreleg
definition: Leg of the prothoracic segment

label: midleg
definition: Leg of the mesothoracic segment

label: hindleg
definition: Leg of the metathoracic segment

label: eye
definition: An organ that detects light

label: shell
definition: A rigid covering that envelops an object

label: genitalia
definition: The outer sex organs

label: skull
definition: The part of the head consisting entirely of cranium and mandible

label: cranium
definition: Upper portion of the skull

label: mandible
definition: A dentary bone that is the only bone in one of the lateral halves of the lower jaw

label: fin
definition: An external projection of an aquatic animal used in propelling or guiding the body

label: egg
definition: The hard-shelled reproductive body produced by an animal

label: bud
definition: An undeveloped shoot system

label: underground structure
definition: Underground plant parts having unspecified morphology

label: root
definition: A plant axis lacking shoot nodes and having indeterminate growth

label: corm
definition: An underground shoot system consisting of a short, enlarged stem and buds

label: tuber
definition: A radially enlarged underground plant axis

label: rhizome
definition: A swollen, horizontal underground shoot axis

label: bulb
definition: An underground shoot system having a short stem and bud enclosed by fleshy leaves
